    <h1>How do I supposed to import everytime?!??!?!</h1>
        <p>HOW?!</p>
        <p>in your <code>/tsconfig.json</code> right at root of your project, inside <code>compilerOptions</code> Dictionary, there is <code>paths</code> Dictionary.<br/> 
            Look at the example at <a href="https://github.com/Perkedel/perkedel-astro/blob/main/tsconfig.json" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a> for how to add yours<br/>
            Also have a look at <a href="https://docs.astro.build/en/guides/aliases/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Astro Aliases</a> for more information about Path Aliases.<br/>
